[after have sex with her psychiatrist]
You know what? This might qualify as sexual harassment.

[after wripping off her clothes and straddling her psychiatrist's chair]
I understand your pain, Jonathan.
Jonathan, we must have sex immediately!

[on Laura]
She ain't the only one who's sexually repressed.
I just felt that with you by my side I could handle anything that life threw at me.
